snippet.textDisplay: I'm a Healthcare worker and I feel so blessed to be one. However, with this virus, I have not been able to see my folks due to fear of getting them sick. My heart has been breaking and I have been trying not to lose my sanity with this social isolation, as I am a major social butterfly. I miss my folks, my coworkers, my friends. I have cried, gotten little or too much sleep, and my depression level has increased. Video chats help, but it's not the same. Regardless, this song really put a smile on my face lol. Thank you for making this! God bless and protect everyone as we work to get through this together! Stay safe and healthy! It'll be over soon! 😎
